---
title: Oven-Ready Chili Coconut Curry Chicken with Carrot-Speckled Rice (trays included)
description: We can never resist a creamy, aromatic coconut curry, which is why we were over the moon when our chefs created this version. It’s got tender chicken breast strips in a creamy, spicy, sweet, and savory sauce, all served over carrot-speckled rice with fresh cilantro and lime juice for brightness. The best part? It’s ready in just 25 minutes from start to finish—and since we’re sending our oven-ready aluminum trays, cleanup is a breeze, too. Talk about a dinner winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-ready-chili-coconut-curry-chicken-8ac0e498.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/oven-ready-chili-coconut-curry-chicken-601049d024f98e74f255ba3b-b4da2a4c.pdf
cuisine: Asian
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/oven-ready-chili-coconut-curry-chicken-601049d024f98e74f255ba3b
course: main course
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
  fat: 30 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
  carbohydrates: 59 g
